OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Police racism' claim over 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fface recognition tech      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Civil rights groups have claimed facial
OL,6, recognition technology will make racism
OL,7, within the police worse.               
OL,9,FSouth Wales Police is set to start     
OL,10,Freusing the controversial technology   
OL,11,Fafter an independent review said it was
OL,12,Fnot discriminatory.                    
OL,14,FBut Liberty said history showed it     
OL,15,Fwould "always be used                  
OL,16,Fdisproportionately against communities 
OL,17,Fof colour".                            
OL,19,FThe force insisted the technology would
OL,20,Fbe used responsibly.                   
